
The BORE 6.1.y ~ 6.3.y introduced a regression
For now, apply upstream fixes to BORE 5.9.6

Results from 9800X3D machine with stress-ng -c 128 (8x CPU saturation)

 BORE update > BORE 5.9.6 > EEVDF > BORE 6.3.2 > BORE 6.1.1
 0.3s          0.5s         1.5s    3.0s         4.5s

 $ for i in $(seq 1 5); do time bash -ilc true; done

 real    0m0.299s
 user    0m0.144s
 sys     0m0.015s

 real    0m0.300s
 user    0m0.149s
 sys     0m0.010s

 real    0m0.273s
 user    0m0.144s
 sys     0m0.014s

 real    0m0.270s
 user    0m0.143s
 sys     0m0.015s

 real    0m0.271s
 user    0m0.141s
 sys     0m0.015s

